* Improved the performance of Windows MDM profile reconciliation during team transfers and bulk profile changes by moving reconciliation out of the synchronous API path. Windows profile reconciliation now runs in the `mdm_windows_profile_manager` cron (which already computes the full desired-vs-actual diff globally), rather than inline under `BulkSetPendingMDMHostProfiles`. This prevents long-running team transfers from holding row locks on `host_mdm_windows_profiles` and starving concurrent MDM / osquery host checkins.
